{"tid":202644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又出招）張炳良擬將部分私樓地轉建公屋應付短期需求","createTime":"2017-04-15T16:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T04:23:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d47bcfcadbb3dfee71468b2d9c47e03d9ce62a9c","tid":202644,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"私根又借勢爆升 政府好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長張炳良表示，政府在多區提出新房屋項目時都遇到居民反對，認為市民要作取捨才可解決房屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良指出，發展商興建「納米樓」是因應樓價高的情況，若不增加房屋供應，難以解決「納米樓」問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他稱，可考慮將部分私營房屋用地，轉作興建公營房屋，應付短期需求。"},{"pid":"86041046d53b22031388dbdd8384ef4b70cd074a","tid":202644,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私樓又借勢爆升 政府好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長張炳良表示，政府在多區提出新房屋項目時都遇到居民反對，認為市民要作取捨才可解決房屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良指出，發展商興建「納米樓」是因應樓價高的情況，若不增加房屋供應，難以解決「納米樓」問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他稱，可考慮將部分私營房屋用地，轉作興建公營房屋，應付短期需求。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cfc6d2c9112ba3101b875f148a594dddd05cd768","tid":202644,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d691ba7e5485d0e0a7fe10f7bab2a389fefcc06c","tid":202644,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T00:42:05.000Z","msg":"收起所有私人地起資助房屋咪篤爆個市囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c922fd64df2f4e6f238470fd7962d5b4f92b571","tid":202644,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"咪又係分比支那狗"},{"pid":"1d83d8f87e3f15b3855232fd147560eab961f692","tid":202644,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"起公屋 黎做咩<br />\n正常香港人都唔會合資格住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aec2a485e32acc883ac69ee02e7f1fad58737f","tid":202644,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收起所有私人地起資助房屋咪篤爆個市囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔合資格住資助房屋而有住屋需求班人點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係人都知要合資格住資助房屋條線係幾咁on9地低<br />\n你即係迫9果班人租貴樓、買貴樓，咁都唔係谷樓市係咩"},{"pid":"7e06b53c33b87db397606b23095510b1ced3e21e","tid":202644,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係賣地條款入面加入出售期限得唔得？"},{"pid":"195dea52d93be57b9f491c4e5a1478970286e8a3","tid":202644,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係賣地條款入面加入出售期限得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n自由市場"},{"pid":"ba2ca23eb079fd86adc6a1ed9b159fa67877986d","tid":202644,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係賣地條款入面加入出售期限得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n自由市場</blockquote><br />\n引入空置稅同第二單位銷售及印花稅就解決好多問題，但政府一定唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1322fb8536221f906e71a961ff72a85ed74283","tid":202644,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係賣地條款入面加入出售期限得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n自由市場</blockquote><br />\n引入空置稅同第二單位銷售及印花稅就解決好多問題，但政府一定唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /